    <string name="amoled_service_name">SwiftSense: AMOLED Screen Protection</string>
    <string name="amoled_service_description">This service is used ONLY to draw a protective pixel overlay on your screen to prevent AMOLED burn-in. It DOES NOT collect, store or transmit any of your personal data, screen content, or keystrokes. It only requires overlay permission to extend your display\'s lifespan.</string>

